ar-subscribe\";N;}}}','yes'),(181,'safecss_rev','11','yes'),(183,'zerif_pro_expires','no','yes'),(186,'zerif_pro_license_status','valid','yes'),(188,'zerif_pro_license','fbcad5f89123e398defadbf8a639fc60','yes'),(191,'WPLANG','','yes'),(192,'new_admin_email','joe@advertisingbros.com','yes'),(199,'theme_switched_via_customizer','','yes'),(203,'limit_login_retries','a:2:{s:13:\"195.242.80.27\";i:1;s:13:\"37.115.32.246\";i:1;}','no'),(204,'limit_login_retries_valid','a:2:{s:13:\"195.242.80.27\";i:1433766610;s:13:\"37.115.32.246\";i:1433780502;}','no'),(266,'theme_mods_zerif-pro','a:73:{i:0;b:0;s:20:\"zerif_bigtitle_title\";s:119:\"THESE DAYS EVERYONE IS SHOUTING TO BE HEARD.<br /><br />At Advertising Brothers, we think great work speaks for itself.\";s:30:\"zerif_bigtitle_redbutton_label\";s:7:\"Read On\";s:32:\"zerif_bigtitle_greenbutton_label\";s:8:\"I\'m Sold\";s:30:\"zerif_bigtitle_greenbutton_url\";s:8:\"#contact\";s:22:\"zerif_aboutus_subtitle\";s:29:\"Here\'s what we can do for you\";s:26:\"zerif_aboutus_biglefttitle\";s:27:\"Yes, we\'re really brothers.\";s:18:\"zerif_aboutus_text\";s:538:\"We started our own marketing business because we got tired of watching good people like you get overcharged for cookie-cutter products and services.<br /><br />We give our clients our mobile phone numbers because we feel strongly that a brand is only as good as the people behind it.<br /><br />Together, we have achieved results for law firms, technology companies, veterinary practices, property management companies, business publications, insurance companies, web hosting providers and many more. Let\'s talk about how we can help you.\";s:28:\"zerif_aboutus_feature1_title\";s:18:\"Marketing Strategy\";s:27:\"zerif_aboutus_feature1_text\";s:144:\"We\'re seasoned marketing professionals who take pride in our strategic approach to your business. Its unique and it should be marketed that way.\";s:25:\"zerif_aboutus_feature1_nr\";s:3:\"100\";s:28:\"zerif_aboutus_feature2_title\";s:17:\"Digital Marketing\";s:27:\"zerif_aboutus_feature2_text\";s:157:\"Our approach to your digital marketing is simple but powerful. We focus on the essentials: Website Design, SEO, PPC, SMM, Email Marketing &amp; Re-targeting.\";s:25:\"zerif_aboutus_feature2_nr\";s:3:\"100\";s:28:\"zerif_aboutus_feature3_title\";s:14:\"Graphic Design\";s:27:\"zerif_aboutus_feature3_text\";s:99:\"Brian knows his way around the Adobe Creative Cloud, and has a team of designers when we need help.\";s:25:\"zerif_aboutus_feature3_nr\";s:2:\"50\";s:28:\"zerif_aboutus_feature4_title\";s:32:\"Website Management &amp; Geekery\";s:27:\"zerif_aboutus_feature4_text\";s:98:\"Joe speaks fluent geek, managing all things technical and in code for the company and our clients.\";s:25:\"zerif_aboutus_feature4_nr\";s:2:\"50\";s:22:\"zerif_ourteam_subtitle\";s:87:\"The number of titles per employee is inversely proportional to the number of employees.\";s:23:\"zerif_testimonials_show\";b:1;s:23:\"zerif_bottomribbon_text\";s:13:\"Already sold?\";s:30:\"zerif_bottomribbon_buttonlabel\";s:12:\"Get in touch\";s:29:\"zerif_bottomribbon_buttonlink\";s:8:\"#contact\";s:22:\"zerif_ribbonright_text\";s:15:\"What about now?\";s:29:\"zerif_ribbonright_buttonlabel\";s:10:\"Contact us\";s:28:\"zerif_ribbonright_buttonlink\";s:8:\"#contact\";s:21:\"zerif_contactus_title\";s:10:\"Let\'s Talk\";s:24:\"zerif_contactus_subtitle\";s:133:\"Talk isn\'t only cheap, it\'s free. We\'ll discuss your goals and how we may be able to help before we even ask for payment information.\";s:20:\"zerif_googlemap_show\";b:0;s:23:\"zerif_googlemap_address\";s:16:\"Mount Laurel, NJ\";s:22:\"zerif_googlemap_static\";b:1;s:22:\"zerif_latest_news_show\";b:0;s:10:\"zerif_logo\";s:86:\"http://advertisingbrothers.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/AB-HORZ-Final-Logo_SMALL.png\";s:23:\"zerif_ourfocus_subtitle\";s:33:\"Here are the things that drive us\";s:28:\"zerif_bigtitle_redbutton_url\";s:6:\"#focus\";s:20:\"zerif_ourfocus_title\";s:30:\"<a name=\"focus\"></a> Our Focus\";s:21:\"zerif_socials_twitter\";s:38:\"http://twitter.com/advertisingbrothers\";s:22:\"zerif_socials_linkedin\";s:40:\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/4857355\";s:24:\"zerif_socials_googleplus\";s:51:\"https://plus.google.com/113818592337118382038/about\";s:16:\"background_image\";s:71:\"http://advertisingbrothers.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/IMG_06273.jpg\";s:17:\"background_repeat\";s:9:\"no-repeat\";s:21:\"background_position_x\";s:6:\"center\";s:21:\"background_attachment\";s:5:\"fixed\";s:25:\"zerif_bigtitle_background\";s:16:\"rgba(0,0,0,0.01)\";s:21:\"zerif_contactus_email\";s:24:\"info@advertisingbros.com\";s:23:\"zerif_contactus_sitekey\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"zerif_email\";s:28:\"info@advertisingbrothers.com\";s:11:\"zerif_phone\";s:12:\"215-253-7146\";s:13:\"zerif_address\";s:16:\"Mount Laurel, NJ\";s:39:\"zerif_bigtitle_1button_background_color\";s:7:\"#dd3333\";s:45:\"zerif_bigtitle_1button_background_color_hover\";s:7:\"#bc0600\";s:39:\"zerif_bigtitle_2button_background_color\";s:7:\"#1a1ef2\";s:45:\"zerif_bigtitle_2button_background_color_hover\";s:7:\"#1b07b5\";s:30:\"zerif_buttons_background_color\";s:7:\"#1a1ef2\";s:36:\"zerif_buttons_background_color_hover\";s:7:\"#1a1ef2\";s:20:\"zerif_footer_socials\";s:7:\"#ffffff\";s:26:\"zerif_footer_socials_hover\";s:7:\"#1a1ef2\";s:31:\"zerif_titles_bottomborder_color\";s:7:\"#e96656\";s:23:\"zerif_ribbon_background\";s:20:\"rgba(221,51,51,0.25)\";s:30:\"zerif_ribbon_button_background\";s:7:\"#1a1ef2\";s:36:\"zerif_ribbon_button_background_hover\";s:7:\"#1b07b5\";s:28:\"zerif_ribbonright_background\";s:20:\"rgba(221,51,51,0.25)\";s:35:\"zerif_ribbonright_button_background\";s:7:\"#1a1ef2\";s:41:\"zerif_ribbonright_button_background_hover\";s:7:\"#1b07b5\";s:28:\"zerif_ribbonright_text_color\";s:7:\"#ffffff\";s:32:\"zerif_contacus_button_background\";s:7:\"#1a1ef2\";s:25:\"zerif_contacus_background\";s:16:\"rgba(0,0,0,0.35)\";s:38:\"zerif_contacus_button_background_hover\";s:7:\"#1b07